{"type": "article", "id": 16288, "title": "Pillow Stool", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-20T06:30:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003457lOygxDzUEkGpJAF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这把用钢铁做的椅子有一个两层的座位，勾勒出像枕头一样的弯曲弧度，冲淡了钢铁本身的金属感，给人舒服和放松的感受。上下两层的铁棒方向相反，重叠看上去就像交织成网格，光从不同方向照射过来，能投射出不同形状的网格纹路，且富有变化。此外，两层中间空间也是放杂志的好地方。<a href=\"http://www.hongyingguo.com/71945/632231/work/pillow-stool\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143612mMz8jltRJaoBZhVy.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"818\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143613rQ2Uwvan5MtbdEKR.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143614hw9KjqNur4mIRbpa.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143614DjIfsuzBPMCUJWRX.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}